@startuml
title US222
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as Operator
participant "System" as Sys

activate Operator
Operator -> Sys : GET /api/maintenance/alerts?type={type}
activate Sys
note right of Sys : type is optional ("FLIGHT_HOURS" or "CALENDAR_DAYS")
Sys --> Operator : Returns list of pending maintenance alerts (200 OK / 204 No Content)
deactivate Sys
deactivate Operator
@enduml